description: Erection of a part 14, part 17-storey tower plus basement and roof enclosure (max. 71.525m above OS Datum), a 31-storey tower plus basement and roof enclosures (max. 116.620m above OS Datum) together with podium level providing for: 304 residential units; 677 sq.m of flexible mixed use commercial floor space (use classes A1, A2, A3, A4, A5 and B1); car parking for up to 80 cars and ancillary plant room.
decision_conditions:
CONDITION: Notwithstanding the approved drawings full details and scaled drawings of any 'shop' front installation within the ground floor commercial element hereby approved shall be submitted to and approved in writing by the Local Planning Authority prior to the first occupation of that unit. The proposed designs shall not incorporate any internal or external roller shutters.

REASON: To ensure that the Local Planning Authority may be satisfied with the external appearance of the building in accordance with policies: Env12; D1; D3; and D4 of the Islington Unitary Development Plan 2002 and policies: 4B.1; 4B.2; and 4B.10 of the London Plan 2008.
